## JQL Quick Reference

```jql
# All active bugs
project = KAN AND component = Bugs AND status != Done

# All active tasks
project = KAN AND component = Tasks AND status != Done

# High priority bugs
project = KAN AND component = Bugs AND priority = High

# Everything in SecureVault
project = KAN
```

## MCP Configuration

The Atlassian MCP server is configured in `cline_mcp_settings.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "github.com/pashpashpash/mcp-atlassian": {
      "command": "mcp-atlassian",
      "args": [],
      "env": {
        "JIRA_URL": "https://aryanbhisikar02.atlassian.net",
        "JIRA_USERNAME": "aryanbhisikar02@gmail.com",
        "JIRA_API_TOKEN": "<stored-in-config>"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

